ersburg]], [[Samara, Russia|Samara]], [[Ufa]], [[Ekaterinburg]], [[Chelyabinsk]]\n| {{flag|Russia}}, {{flag|Ukraine}}, {{flag|Kazakhstan}}, {{flag|Finland}}, {{flag|Sweden}}, {{flag|Netherlands}}, {{flag|Germany}}\n| 2009\n| 587<ref name=he-dataix>{{cite web|url= https://bgp.he.net/report/exchanges |title= Internet Exchange Report \u00a0| publisher = Hurricane Electric Internet Services |accessdate=2019-11-13}}</ref>\n| 3,380<ref>{{cite web|author=DATA-IX |url=http://www.dataix.ru/members/ |title=DATA-IX |publisher=data-ix.ru |date= |accessdate=2018-11-11}}</ref>\n| 2,320\n| {{date|2020-03-31}}\n|-\n| [[France-IX]]\n| France-IX<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.franceix.net/ |title=France-IX |publisher=France-IX |date= |accessdate=2016-02-10}}</ref>\n| [[Paris]], [[Marseille]]\n| {{flag|France}}\n| 2010\n| 427<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.franceix.net/en/members-resellers/members/ |title=France IX members list |publisher=France-IX |date= |accessdate=2019-08-29}}</ref>\n| 1,530<ref name=\"franceixstats\">{{cite web|url=https://www.franceix.net/en/technical/traffic-statistics/ |title=Traffic statistics |publisher=France-IX |date= |accessdate=2019-08-29}}</ref>\n| 1,059<ref name=\"franceixstats\" />\n| {{date|2020-03-31|}}\n|-\n| [[Netnod Internet Exchange i Sverige|Netnod]]\n| Netnod Internet Exchange in Sweden<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.netnod.se/ |title=Netnod |publisher=Netnod.se |date= |accessdate=2020-03-18}}</ref>\n| [[Stockholm]], [[Copenhagen]], [[Sundsvall]], [[Gothenburg]], [[Lule\u00e5]]\n| {{flag|Sweden}}, {{flag|Denmark}}\n| 1997\n| 269<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.netnod.se/ix/networks |title=IX Networks |publisher=Netnod.se |date= |accessdate=2011-10-11}}</ref><ref name=\"netnod\">Includes all 6 sites: Stockholm, Copenhagen, Sundsvall, Gothenburg, and Lule\u00e5</ref>\n| 2,277<ref name=\"netnod\" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.netnod.se/ix-stats/sums/All.html|title=Aggregate traffic graphs All |publisher=netnod.se |date= |accessdate=2020-03-18}}<